@startuml StateMachineDiagram

[*] --> Idle

Idle --> DomainSelected : select domain

DomainSelected --> LoadingDomainKnowledge
LoadingDomainKnowledge --> GeneratingQuestions
GeneratingQuestions --> QuestionsReady

QuestionsReady --> AnsweringQuestions

AnsweringQuestions --> SubmittingResponses : submit answers
AnsweringQuestions --> Idle : back
SubmittingResponses --> StoringResponses
StoringResponses --> Completed

Completed --> Role : select or insert role

@enduml
